            Graph the product of the lines you found in <xref ref="exer-share-x"/>. How does the product compare with the graph of the quadratic function given in standard form? If the graphs are not the same, adjust this equation so the graphs coincide. Compare the equation in factored form with the equation in standard form. What do these equations have in common?
          </p>
        </statement>
      </task>

      <task>
        <statement>
